body.name: Taegila Small Portable Charger iPhone 5000mAh with Built in Cable, MFi Certified Compact Power Bank with LCD Display & LED Light for All iPhone Series 14/13/12/11/XR/X/SE/8/7/6 Pro Max (Black)

【Adjustable 4 Modes LED Light】 The portable battery charger has LED lantern that can be switched to 3 colors of warm - white - warm white, you can use it as fill light for selfies and flashlight in the dark. In additional the SOS flashing mode is designed for emergency, you can clearly send out a distress signal to get rescue in the case of distress.

【For All iPhone and AirPods】Portable Charger has an integrated connector and battery, can charge all your devices with this one battery pack charger, it's about the size of a car key weighs 92g, you can charge while gaming or calling. Widely compatible with iPhone 14 14 Pro Max 13 13 Pro Max 12 12 Mini 12 Pro Max 11Pro XS XR X 8 7 6 Plus Airpods and so on.

【Fast Recharging Function】Recharging the cell phone charger for 50% power within 30 mins with provided USB C cable and adapter(not included), which can charge your iPhone 13 from 20% to 60% without using the phone. It's equipped with the latest heat insulation chip to prevent overheating, moreover, it supports pass-through charging which allows you to charge the smartphone while charging the charger itself.

【Customer Satisfaction】We have a professional after-sales team, if you have any questions, please feel free to contact us. The Taegila thinner and smaller charger adds convenience to charging on the way, toss it into your bag which will ensure reliable charging for your iPhone wherever you are: home, travel, hiking, fishing, on the plane, etc. it's about the size of a car key weighs 92g, dimensions is only 76*46*24.7mm (2.99''x1.8''x0.97''), you can charge while gaming or calling.

【What You Will Get】: 1*portable charger, 1*USB-C charge cable, 1*user manual. Normally, if your phone case thickness more than 4mm, you'd better remove your phone case to charge your iPhone. Notice: Please fully charge the power bank after using up the power at the first time to protect the battery and extend the battery life of the power bank

reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars BEST PORTABLE CHARGER I HAVE USED!

Here's why it deserves a solid 5 stars:Bulky Case Friendly: The fact that it's compatible with bulky cases is a game-changer for me. I no longer have to remove my case every time I need a charge. This feature alone is a huge win.Built-In Flashlight: The built-in flashlight is a small but incredibly useful addition. It's come in handy more times than I can count. Whether I'm searching for something in my bag or navigating a dark space, it's proven to be a lifesaver.User-Friendly Design: The button on the side for power control is a brilliant touch. It's easy to locate and operate, making it a hassle-free experience. No need for complicated instructions or setup.Lightning-Fast Charging: The speed at which this power bank charges is mind-blowing. It takes my phone from empty to full in less than 2 hours, which is a total game-changer for my busy lifestyle.Pocket-Friendly Size: The compact size is perfect for on-the-go use. It easily fits in my pocket or bag without adding unnecessary bulk. This makes it incredibly convenient for travel, commuting, or just daily errands.Overall, the Taegila Portable Charger has exceeded my expectations on every front. Its compatibility with bulky cases, built-in flashlight, user-friendly design, lightning-fast charging, and compact size make it an absolute must-have for anyone in need of a reliable power bank. I'm thoroughly impressed and couldn't be happier with my purchase!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 9, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars A Compact and Reliable Charging Solution!
reviews.reviewText: I recently purchased the power bank for charging my phone, and I couldn't be happier with its performance. The compact design makes it incredibly portable, allowing me to easily slip it into my pocket or bag without any bulkiness. One of the features of this power bank is its impressive charging capacity. With this power bank, I can charge my phone multiple times on a single charge. It's a lifesaver, especially during long commutes or travels when access to a power outlet is limited. Furthermore, the build quality is top-notch. The power bank feels solid and well-constructed, providing me with confidence in its durability. The sleek design adds a touch of elegance, making it a stylish accessory to carry around. Additionally, the intelligent charging technology incorporated in this power bank is a game-changer. It automatically detects the optimal charging speed for my phone, preventing any potential damage from overcharging. This feature gives me peace of mind knowing that my device is safe and protected. The battery indicator is another useful feature that deserves mentioning. It accurately shows the remaining power, allowing me to plan my charging needs accordingly. It's a small detail, but it makes a big difference in ensuring that I never run out of power unexpectedly. Overall, I highly recommend this power bank for anyone in need of a reliable and efficient charging solution.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 29, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Very portable & great for emergencies
reviews.reviewText: The portable charger arrived pretty fast (thanks to Amazon Prime). It was only 80% charged when I opened it but it took less than 30 minutes to have it fully (100%) charged. I got this for my wife as she works long shifts & doesn't have a chance to recharge her iPhone and so this is a life saver for her. I just have to make sure she charges this as well as her iPhone when she gets home.This is a very compact charger, almost a size of a lipstick tube & its very smooth all around making it perfect to drop it in her side pockets (or purse) & its 4800mAh capacity is good enough to charge her phone for at least once when she runs out of juice in the afternoon. This is supposedly MFi certified which hopefully means that it would continue working 'till the charger's battery is completely depleted and not when the Lightening interface stops working as it has been with many of my iPhone charger cables.The charger comes with a USB-C cable but no adapter which means you have to use your own adapter which I recommend to be 2 amp. The max DC voltage is 5 volt and so the adapter would be 10w charger. Using my 2A charger, it initially went from 80 to 100% in less than 30 minutes and in another occasion after it reached 20%, it took less than 2 hours to fully charge it.I don't have the tools to ascertain for sure that this is in fact a 4800 mAh battery bank but on one occasion when the iPhone was down to only 10% capacity, it did fully charge my iPhone & still was showing 25% battery left; my iPhone 12 has a 2815 mAh battery and so I was thinking that the battery bank should at least be at 50% but then there are other factors that can affect battery storage capacity such as temperature or age of the battery so I'm not making any conclusion here other than saying that it would at least fully charge your iPhone once but not your iPad (8th or 9th Gen) but then again it wasn't really meant for those devices.The charger also comes with a light mode. It's activated by pressing & holding the button on side of the unit for 1-2s to turn it on & then clicking again to switch the light color from warm to white & to warm white, the last one would be a SOS mode with lights flashing. The lights might be a plus for some but I think it's more of a gimmick as iPhone has a working light that works just fine.I would be careful using this with a thick case especially those that covers the charging port. I have a light silicon case that has ample room to allow the lightning connection but I doubt it would work for most Otterbox (like the defender series) or full protective cases out there.In the end, this is meant for those who want a very light emergency power-bank & not a true power-bank that can charge your iPad or even non-apple devices. it's an elegant solution @ a reasonable cost but if you're expecting an all around solution for anything else, you should look elsewhere.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 6, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great stocking stuffer
reviews.reviewText: Gave this to my daughter for Christmas and she loves it. It is compact, lightweight and the perfect backup when she's out and her phone starts to run low. You get about one full phone charge when the charger is at 100%. She has a thin cover on her iphone and there is no issue plugging this in. She likes that no additional cord is needed. It takes a couple of hours to power the charger back up when it is at 0.

As an iPhone 11 Pro user, I find its clear LCD display and substantial battery capacity ideal for at least one full charge, making it perfect for daily use. The adjustable LED light with various modes, including an SOS feature, is incredibly useful. Its ultra-portable design and rapid charging capability make it an essential accessory for my iPhone 11 Pro
Works so well. So fast and compact. Love the port protection. Can just keep it in my purse for whenever I need it. It gives me a full battery so quickly and recharges very fast as well. Great buy.

Although battery doesn't seem to have the capacity as specified, but it's still good to carry in my bag.And the design to have a light on it is convenient and important when I want to look for something in my handbag in dark. Overall I like it!

reviews.reviewTitle: Small Portable Charger for iPhone: Compact Power on the Go
reviews.reviewText: The Small Portable Charger for iPhone has become an indispensable companion in my daily life. Its compact size and lightweight design make it the perfect on-the-go charging solution, effortlessly slipping into my pocket or bag without adding any noticeable bulk. What truly sets it apart is its fast charging capability, ensuring that my iPhone is powered up in no time, even when I'm in a rush. The charger's universal compatibility ensures that it will remain useful for future iPhone models, making it a smart long-term investment. Its durable build quality has also impressed me, as it has withstood everyday use without any issues. While its battery capacity is somewhat limited, it serves as an excellent emergency backup when I need a quick top-up. Though it may be a tad pricier than some alternatives, the combination of portability, reliability, and quality make this charger worth every penny.

I love the size of this charger. It is great for one full charge on my phone literally your phone can charge 80% in just 30mins It is a nice size and easy to use even when you want to still charge your phone while using it. Lighter than I expected, comes with a cap to protect the USB-C connector.
